
Recordar que en el scratch se encuentran los folder: 



EnKS_MC_LOTOS  --> Plots sobre states and dc of each of the city plots

EnKS_MC_LOTOS_V2  -->  Calculate cholesky for the states, the parameters and the combination of both

EnKS_MC_LOTOS_V2_locate_background2D  -->  Concatenate and plot the time series for dc and concentrations and prepare the snapshots for the parameters and states

EnKS_MC_LOTOS_V2_ENKF  --> Regresa las covarianzas al dominio 2D



Plot_satelites  -->  Generate plots of the satellite for the North Domain

Plot_satellites_compare  -->  comparison with the Columns of the satellite tropomi INNOVATION  generando problemas

Plot_satellte_sigmas_saving  -->  ERROR PLOTS

